###  http://data.org/615001019/2025-26
<http://data.org/615001019/2025-26> rdf:type owl:NamedIndividual ,
                                             <https://guia.org/CourseGuide> ;
                                    <https://guia.org/hasCompetency> <http://data.org/CE04> ,
                                                                     <http://data.org/CE05> ,
